## Test
```bash
# File must exist and export the three functions
grep -c "export function getPDSServiceUrl" config/pds.ts     # must be 1
grep -c "export function extractDomainFromHandle" config/pds.ts  # must be 1
grep -c "export function extractPrefixFromHandle" config/pds.ts  # must be 1
